,
Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Coal and Steel Community, and in particular  Article 18 thereof,
Whereas by its Decision of 4 March 1996  (1) the Council appointed the members of the Consultative  Committee of the European Coal and Steel Community, except for the Spanish members in the workers  category, for the period ending 3 March 1998;
Whereas by its Decision of 29 March 1996  (2) the Council designated the representative  organizations of Spanish workers required to draw up lists of candidates for the representation of  Spanish workers on the Consultative Committee of the European Coal and Steel Community;
Whereas the Spanish representative organizations designated by the Decision of 29 March 1996 have  submitted their lists of candidates for the workers category;
Whereas the Spanish members in the workers category of the Consultative Committee of the European  Coal and Steel Community should be appointed for a period expiring on 3 March 1998,
